    Ё        STEP 1: INSTALLING THE 4690 APPLICATION            Ё
    Ё                DEBUGGER                                   Ё
    Ё                                                           Ё
    Ё  ON A MULTIPLE CONTROLLER SYSTEM, THE SUBORDINATE         Ё
    Ё  CONTROLLERS MUST BE CONFIGURED TO RECEIVE NON-SYSTEM     Ё
    Ё  COMPOUND FILES.                                          Ё
    Ё                                                           Ё
    Ё     TO INSTALL THE NEW DEBUGGER INSERT DISKETTE #1 INTO   Ё
    Ё  DISKETTE DRIVE A: ON THE MASTER CONTROLLER. THEN, ON THE Ё
    Ё  MASTER CONTROLLER, TYPE IN THE COMMAND:                  Ё
    Ё                                                           Ё
    Ё                  A:INSTALL                                Ё
    Ё                                                           Ё
    Ё     THIS PROGRAM WILL CREATE THE USER LOGICAL NAMES AND   Ё
    Ё  SUBDIRECTORY NEEDED TO RUN THE DEBUGGER ON ALL CONTROL-  Ё
    Ё  LERS. THE LOGICAL NAMES HELP: AND DEBUG: ARE RESERVED    Ё
    Ё  FOR THE DEBUGGER. IF THESE LOGICAL NAMES ARE ALREADY     Ё
    Ё  INSTALLED, THE INSTALL PROGRAM WILL NOT UPDATE THEM.     Ё
    Ё  IF THESE NAMES ARE NOT DEFINED TO THE DEBUG SUBDIRECTORY,Ё
    Ё  THE DEBUGGER MAY NOT OPERATE CORRECTLY. IT WILL ALSO     Ё
    Ё  COPY ALL THE PROGRAM FILES TO THE DEBUG SUBDIRECTORY     Ё
    Ё  ON THE HARD DISK AND THEN DISTRIBUTE THEM.               Ё
    Ё                                                           Ё
